{"tid":1753662,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"本民前: 區議會內的五大訴求","createTime":"2019-11-25T03:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T21:05:45.000Z","uid":7971,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8f23f48a7d93d6250f9c86d25f35ca54820b2bd2","tid":1753662,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:56:58.000Z","msg":"區議會內的五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1. 全部行人路美化成磚路，路邊綠化Planter內加碎石或鵝蛋石。<br />\n2. 大量增設玻璃樽回收桶。<br />\n3. 警察宿舍外欄杆加花盆種水生植物養蚊、正門加設臨時廁所。<br />\n4. 拆晒監控燈柱／CCTV ，公廁更衣室附近不能有CCTV。<br />\n5. 未諗到有冇建議？每區加個易燃物品儲存倉過唔過份？有人話要永久連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n認真Post嚟<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\nSource: 本土民主前線FB"},{"pid":"f8bd961be59702bed0f9a75432f8d883bb715df1","tid":1753662,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:57:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1e2bbc4e64b692c9a26e17dede62c114c310a08b","tid":1753662,"uid":131836,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:57:41.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n請當選區議員用藝術為由(或其他方式)，保留各區連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n一來繼續可以俾大家貼文宣<br />\n<br />\n二來正式運用議會力量將連儂牆寫入政府文件<br />\n<br />\n三來第日拆唔拆就可以由市民話事，唔洗俾政府用行政暴力清牆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28badaa0a23feb2deec994287b720966031160a","tid":1753662,"uid":7971,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"好簡單，唔好咁都唔做，仲要連主席都係自己人"},{"pid":"3cb5b36d1519d334575d40d264b94a043c8e7e05","tid":1753662,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:59:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e3847b16a22fd0e4bbc661d2fa41ebbebb61ba5","tid":1753662,"uid":51111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"(行動post) 今晚poly定十八區商場？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1753155</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"58cb7689c31d404d153dc1e62c18b71165ca3269